<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Corner fragment of an elaborately moulded feature, probably a <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> front (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.115</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.29</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.09</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on two adjacent faces.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>a: ll. 1, 5f., <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.015</measure>; ll. 2-4, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02</measure>; lunate <term lang="grc-Latn">sigma</term> in l.1. b: l.1, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02</measure>; l.2, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.022</measure>; l.3, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.028</measure>; ll.4-5, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.025</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p><date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
